    Technology:
    Shopify Liquid
    responsive CSS
    lightweight GSAP animations
    Sections:
    Hero
    animated headline
    hero image
    CTA button
    Featured Products
    responsive product grid
    hover zoom animation
    Collections
    collection cards
    fade-in animation on scroll
    Newsletter
    simple email signup form
    animated gradient background
    Responsive requirements:
    mobile first layout
    tablet optimized spacing
    desktop grid layouts
    scalable design for ultra-wide screens
    Shopify theme editor settings:
    text
